data.description: Wonderful Northside ranch! Top notch location. Welcome all your people into this well cared for, well laid out, airy, bright, home! Home features newer laminate floors throughout, two bay windows, spacious dining room, breakfast bar, SS Appliances, first floor laundry and nice sized bedrooms. Enjoy your basement retreat with plenty of extra living space perfect for many uses! All glass block windows in LL. I can not say enough about this epic yard! Walk out to your huge deck with a ramp, then check out the beautiful  concrete patio/driveway notice the totally fenced in  private yard screaming for a housewarming party! This is a yard to brag about. Newer roof on house! Gutter guards with warranty, water heater 3yrs old. Near golf, food, schools, lake and parks.
